Although the result of my efforts was nachweislich positive, my government dissent still handles as a faith break and strives for that, political opinion comment to kriminalisieren and to charge.
Nevertheless: To express the truth is not a crime.
I am confident, that the government of the United States with support of the international community will put aside this detrimental attitude.
I hope for my being in the situation if the difficulties of this humanitarian situation are settled me appropriate at the responsible clarification of the facts of affairs concerning the statements made in the media, in particular with regard to truth and authenticity of the reports, and law-appropriate involve.
